          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Unique Action" typeId="ba93-e32d-f1ac-e188">▶ Select one friendly SPECTRE SQUAD operative within this operative’s control range and not within 3&quot; of enemy operatives. That friendly operative can immediately perform a free **Shoot** action (excluding **Guard**), and you can change its order to do so.
